Class AbstractIntersectionResult

  • java.lang.Object
    • jot.physics.AbstractIntersectionResult
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    IntersectionResult

    public abstract class AbstractIntersectionResult
extends java.lang.Object
    Abstract class that must be implemented by a class that implements the a ray-shape intersection result.
    Author:
    G. Amador & A. Gomes
